&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in Civil, Structural, or related field (or equivalent hands-on experience)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;6–10+ years delivering civil/structural/site infrastructure projects that were actually constructed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated track record of real-world scope (e.g., large-scale sites, major concrete/utility work, multi-acre developments)&lt;/li&gt;
